metadata.description:
The Golden NFT is a first of its kind NFT drop that will provide a unique opportunity for seven people across the world to become the exclusive buyers of a never before sold Lonsdale vitola of our famed Andalusian Bull, named #1 Cigar of the Year by Cigar Aficionado in 2016. The Andalusian Bull - The Golden measures 42 x 6 1/4 and has, until now, been a private cigar that Litto and Tony Gomez have kept for themselves. 
 
 **About La Flor Dominicana** 
 
 La Flor Dominicana was founded in 1994 in Santiago, Dominican Republic by husband and wife team Litto and Ines Gomez and remains a family business to this day. Over the years we have developed a wide range of award-winning blends to fulfill the ever-changing needs of today's cigar smoker. Our well-known consistency is made possible because we personally own and operate our farm and factory, giving us a rare level of control over the quality of our products.
